{"tid":1404470,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人想分手但怕寂寞？","createTime":"2019-08-04T04:43:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T21:11:25.000Z","uid":158998,"like":5,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"f2c73a2877b2e614410faf45ade9d17d77ce24ed","tid":1404470,"uid":158998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:43:11.000Z","msg":"男朋友因爲之前呃過我，<br />\n所以搞到我好無安全感。<br />\n其實我唔想原諒佢，<br />\n我覺得一早要分手，<br />\n雖然佢依家好好，<br />\n但佢俾唔到我需要嘅安全感我。<br />\n<br />\n而我亦同佢傾過，<br />\n我直接講我想分手但我怕寂寞，<br />\n佢聽完係無乜嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係每日我都會諗起佢呃過我嘅事，<br />\n每日都會俾呢啲想法圍繞，<br />\n覺得好辛苦，<br />\n我應該點做<br />\n<br />\n利申無乜朋友，有depression，好驚寂寞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n淨係想有人陪"},{"pid":"656d2cc56ecaa8a01ff4500548bd2b8ac2bc9f6a","tid":1404470,"uid":131338,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:44:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7fcfa1e979d5ae6c79e82e96ec175c721beb8e1","tid":1404470,"uid":206003,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:46:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3dc21a12f88d32dc6491994f8757bd909943e81","tid":1404470,"uid":244889,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:47:49.000Z","msg":"好想有人陪<br />\n<br />\n分咗手一年，都不時諗起以前有人慰藉嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n次次發夢都見到好多都有伴一齊去...<br />\n而我卻孤單一人向前去..."},{"pid":"f969d3460bb36b1955f5b463ea6fdff5dc41fe24","tid":1404470,"uid":200604,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:52:47.000Z","msg":"我完全明白<br />\n身同感受<br />\n信仼同安全感真係一但破壞咗<br />\n就好難重建翻<br />\n唔係我唔想信佢<br />\n係我真係迫唔到自己信<br />\n好難移除心中嘅刺"},{"pid":"ec86722286d54b0c6a97aa6befcf5835b3d69680","tid":1404470,"uid":124569,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:53:34